@node "System"


        Copy cando.library to LIBS:.
        Leave Informer in the Mauscheln drawer or move to C:

        You must not do the following things...but probably better

        Set overscan to 700 x 260. Then the screen shouldn't scroll.
        Mauscheln uses a 700 x 520 laced screen.

        This program was written on an emulated OS 3.1, so I guess
        that Mauscheln should run on OS 3.0 and above.
@endnode
